name: cred-rea-fish-team-stationary-point-count-surveys-at-kaui-island-2005
notes: Stationary Point Counts at 4 stations at each survey site were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments conducted at 12 sites at Kaui in July, 2005 from the NOAA vessel Hi'ialakai (HI05-05). Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
